<h1>HOSTEL</h1>
<p>Built up Area of the Ladies Hostel is about 20,000 sq.feet and the Boys Hostel is about 25,000 sq.feet. Hostel Students are provided to use 24 Hours Internet Facility . Library is kept open for their use. Separate hostels for boys and girls. Regularity, puntuality and discipline have been the watch words of our hostel life. Recreations include gymnasium, television, outdoor and indoor sports activities, magazines and internet access.
</p>
